{
  "stem": "18960.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was assigned to a coal mine in-- in Wattenscheid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Watten was near Gelsenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Zeche Holland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Zeche means [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] coal mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The name of the coal mine was Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It has nothing to do with Holland as a country.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But they call it, the coal mine, Zeche Holland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was assigned there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I found-- found myself about 1,500 feet below in the coal mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was really awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Hot.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The air was-- was full of dust-- of coal dust.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When I was coming out from the coal mine and I looked in the mirror, all I saw is my-- the whites of my eyes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Totally black.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The type of work we had to-- were to-- we had to do there-- they were blasting the coal mines.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We were blasting coal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we had to load the blasted coal into little wagons that were rolling along.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Those-- those wagons had to be always full. 10 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was slavery.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] at that time, I did not smoke.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we used to get every month or every two-- two weeks-- I don't remember-- a-- a ration of cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So I befriended the so-called Obersteiger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He was the foreman in the-- in the mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he was also-- he was speaking Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He was speaking German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He was from Silesia, which there were coal mines in-- their-- their experience in coal mines [INAUDIBLE] brought him here, probably.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I was keeping giving him those-- bribing him with my cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He liked me so much that after a while, he tells me, Stefan, I'll give an easier job than this here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Apparently bribery worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And he brought me into a room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It's called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
